query:
ALTER TABLE notificationAnalytics 
  ADD COLUMN channel enum('push','email','sms') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'push' AFTER userId,
  ADD COLUMN bouncedAt timestamp NULL,
  ADD COLUMN bounceReason text NULL,
  ADD COLUMN carrier varchar(100) NULL,
  ADD COLUMN countryCode varchar(10) NULL,
  MODIFY COLUMN deliveryStatus enum('pending','sent','delivered','failed','expired','bounced','undelivered') DEFAULT 'pending'
